notes: This was transferred from a super rare Brazilian 12" PROMO vinyl in MINT condition.

Nirvana guides claim the DAT(1) > CDR in circulation of this date is superior to the Incesticide CD album. No research was done so far comparing Nirvana CD's with Nirvana vinyl's. Vinyl reaches higher frequencies than CD, this HQ PROMO vinyl transfer of "Molly's Lips" sounds superior to my ears !
